text: Gam-COVID-Vac (, romanized: Gam-KOVID-Vak), trade-named Sputnik V, is a COVID-19 vaccine created by the Gamaleya Research Institute of Epidemiology and Microbiology, and registered on 11 August 2020 by the Russian Ministry of Health. Gam-COVID-Vac has been approved for distribution in Russia. ==References== Category:COVID-19 pandemic
title: Gam-COVID-Vac
